================================================================================
                  6. INTELLECTUAL PROPERTY AND PRIORITY OF INVENTION
================================================================================

The Author asserts authorship and priority of invention for the technical
contributions described in the Software, including but not limited to:

  - the canonical SHA-256 descriptor addressing scheme;
  - the Merkle-DAG-style content-addressed node store for tensors;
  - the hybrid low-rank + bitwise XOR residual reconstruction technique;
  - the reversible delta-chain semantics for tensor mutations;
  - the codec-tournament selection over RAW, SPARSE, SVD, and TensorLy
    decomposition strategies.

The publication of this repository constitutes a public, timestamped
disclosure of the foregoing for the purpose of establishing prior art and
authorship attribution.

